Title : Vazhayila
Text : {{Use dmy dates|date=September 2018}}
{{Use Indian English|date=September 2018}}
'''Vazhayila''' is a place near [[Peroorkada]] and located at the outskirts of [[Thiruvananthapuram]], Kerala. The place has St. Jude catholic church. It comes under Vattiyoorkavu mandalam. There are various shopping centers like Meenu bakery, Orange, Sreedevi Stores and JYOTHI Flourmills
There are a famous sports club 
#  Winners Sports arts and village recreation club

